#

Savory Herb Roasted Chicken with Creamy Mushroom Gravy

$20
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

dairychicken

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Tags:

main coursecomfort foodroasted chicken

Description

A succulent roasted chicken infused with fresh herbs, served with a rich and creamy mushroom gravy.

Ingredients

  • whole chicken: 3-4 lbs
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • fresh rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • fresh thyme: 2 sprigs
  • garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • salt: 1 tbsp
  • black pepper: 1 tsp
  • cremini mushrooms: 8 oz, sliced
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • chicken broth: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • flour: 2 tbsp
